that all animals can be tamed,

02:10.520 --> 02:14.080
the secret is to be nice at times
and mean at others,

02:14.160 --> 02:16.440
so they don't understand.

02:16.520 --> 02:20.480
As my brother and I are equal,
we share the tasks:

02:20.560 --> 02:22.760
one is nice and one is mean.

02:25.160 --> 02:27.360
I bet you're the mean one.

02:28.720 --> 02:30.560
You bet right.

02:31.560 --> 02:35.960
But I'll be nice to you,
if you'll be my digging dog.

02:36.040 --> 02:38.360
Are you sure you're the mean one?

02:40.040 --> 02:42.280
I remember at school

02:42.360 --> 02:45.320
they called you
the asshole and the dumbass.

02:46.360 --> 02:48.040
I think you're the dumbass.

02:53.480 --> 02:55.600
No, stop it!

03:01.280 --> 03:03.320
Remember when you came to the store?

03:04.320 --> 03:06.480
You never said hello to us.

03:07.480 --> 03:10.440
