03:37.840 --> 03:40.040
Fuck you!

03:40.120 --> 03:42.040
What a weird world,

03:42.160 --> 03:45.280
now you're the dog
and I'm your master.

04:04.000 --> 04:06.240
C'mon, we've got to escape.

05:16.000 --> 05:18.320
Dig, bitch.

05:18.400 --> 05:20.000
What for?

05:20.840 --> 05:23.400
