- No.

05:31.400 --> 05:36.320
I'm a "morass", a cross between
a moron and a dumbass.

05:45.440 --> 05:46.760
Go on, dig!

06:08.120 --> 06:11.280
Eat up, it's with venison and potatoes.

06:35.280 --> 06:37.320
