07:47.720 --> 07:49.640
You're really hungry, aren't you?

08:00.000 --> 08:01.680
Look what I got for you.

08:07.400 --> 08:09.200
Good girl.

08:10.120 --> 08:12.120
Want another piece?

08:23.080 --> 08:26.280
See? A little mean and a little nice.

08:45.640 --> 08:48.200
Soon the world will be all mine,

08:49.280 --> 08:50.640
